These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, trance, house, jazz
House: townhouse, futuristic, cottage, farmhouse
1. the fan of jazz is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
3. the futuristic house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of house is on the right of the cottage house##1
5. the farmhouse house is between the futuristic house and the cottage house##2
6. the fan of jazz is the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | r&b     | house | trance |
| House     | townhouse     | cottage | farmhouse  | futuristic      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, drama, horror, documentary
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, domino, monopoly
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing monopoly is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | drama    | documentary     | horror  |
| Game     | mah-jongg    | domino | snooker | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
House: wooden, victorian, futuristic, tower
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, drama, spy
1. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
2. the victorian house is on the far left##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
5. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| House   | victorian   | futuristic   | wooden  | tower |
| Movie-Genre           | crime | spy | drama | action  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, iced-tea, lemonade, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, swimming, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is swimming##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | milk | juice | lemonade  |
| Sport   | parkour  | snowboarding   | cricket  | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, golf, parkour, basketball
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, yellow, aquamarine, black
1. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who likes black is the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Sport   | baseball    | golf   | parkour | basketball    |
| Color      | yellow | light-blue | aquamarine       | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, epic, adventure, satire
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, zucchini, radish, plum
1. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person eating radish is between the person eating plum and the person watching adventure movies##2
3. the person eating watermelon is between the person eating radish and the person watching superhero movies##2
4. the person eating plum is on the far right##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero | adventure | satire | epic |
| Food   | zucchini | watermelon  | radish    | plum  |

