.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, zinnia, tulip
House: tower, ranch-style, futuristic, victorian
1. the victorian house is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left or far right##3
3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsrose and the person who growstulip##2
5. the ranch-style house is the ranch-style house##1
6. the ranch-style house is between the futuristic house and the person who growstulip##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Flower   | bellflower | tulip | zinnia | rose     |
| House     | tower | victorian  | ranch-style   | futuristic |

