There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, german, indian, polish
1. the indonesian is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the cottage house is the german##1
3. the cottage house is on the left of the indian##1
4. the cottage house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the palace house is on the left of the tower house##1
6. the german is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| House         | cottage | colonial | palace | tower   |
| Nationality   | german | indian | indonesian      | polish |

