.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, horror, western, musical
City: paris, prague, liverpool, boston
1. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to boston is the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person watching horror movies is between the person traveling to prague and the person traveling to paris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre     | time-travel | horror   | western      | musical      |
| City   | prague     | liverpool | paris | boston |

