.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, librarian, fisherman, nurse
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, may, september, april
1. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the fisherman is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in may##2
3. the librarian is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the nurse is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Job   | accountant | librarian | fisherman      | nurse   |
| Birthday   | september  | may    | july | april |

