.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
House: gothic-revival, wooden, tower, ranch-style
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, apricot, yellow, black
1. the wooden house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
2. the wooden house is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person who likes black is the tower house##1
4. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
5. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
6. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| House       | gothic-revival | tower | ranch-style    | wooden      |
| Color   | yellow       | black       | apricot | emerald |

