.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, water-polo, rugby, lacrosse
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, cranberry, kale, strawberry
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
4. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
6. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
7. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | volleyball | rugby  | lacrosse | water-polo |
| Food           | kale     | strawberry | nectarine    | cranberry     |

