.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, airplane, quad-bike, motorbike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, zombie, drama, thriller
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person watching zombie movies##3
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Transport   | airplane  | scooter | motorbike  | quad-bike      |
| Movie-Genre    | thriller | mystery | drama | zombie |

