.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, cain, dannemann, ritmeester
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, police-officer, pilot, doctor
1. the doctor is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the doctor##3
3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the pilot##3
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the scientist is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Cigar   | davidoff | ritmeester | dannemann | cain |
| Job         | police-officer  | pilot   | doctor | scientist     |

