There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, aquamarine, white, fuchsia
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left of the fan of folk##1
