.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, train, ship, scooter
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, dancing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Transport   | train     | motorbike     | ship          | scooter |
| Hobby      | woodworking | collecting | gardening | dancing  |

 